FBIS4-59430 "drnes093_j_94002" FBIS-NES-94-093 Daily Report 12 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Citizens Residing in `Vicinity' of al-Ahmar Gang Warned Citizens Residing in `Vicinity' of al-Ahmar Gang Warned EA1205190894 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 1650 GMT 12 May 94 EA1205190894 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Text] Respected listeners: Here is an announcement. The forces of unity, democracy, and modernization notify brother citizens residing in the vicinity of the bloody al-Ahmar gang and their supporters in Sanaa, Ta'izz, and al-Hudaydah to temporarily vacate in order to avoid injury arising from the crimes of the members of this bloody (?killer) family that ignited the fires of total war against our people and their honorable and loyal forces. The homes of this odious family are deemed to be military targets of the forces of unity, democracy, and modernization. The members of this family will be pursued, wherever they may be.
